The paper proposes a matrix decomposition framework for data integration and pattern discovery, which is a common topic in machine learning and data mining. The paper also explicitly models the heterogeneity of noise in multi-view data, which is a specific problem in this field. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), and cs.IT (Information Theory).
